          Dump Log  ${ON_ACCESS_LOG_PATH}
          Remove File    ${ON_ACCESS_LOG_PATH}
          Run Keyword If   ${ON_ACCESS_PLUGIN_HANDLE}   Restart On Access
    END


Dump and Reset Logs
